: vertical; -webkit-line-clamp: 2; margin: 0px;\">Đã bao gồm ưu đãi trong giá tour</p></div></div>','','<span style=\"color: rgb(23, 23, 23); font-family: __Inter_f367f3, __Inter_Fallback_f367f3; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\">- Xe tham quan (16, 29, 35, 45 chỗ tùy theo số lượng khách)</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: __Inter_f367f3, __Inter_Fallback_f367f3; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248); margin: 0.5rem 0px; color: rgb(23, 23, 23); text-align: justify; background-image: initial !important; background-position: initial !important; background-size: initial !important; background-repeat: initial !important; background-attachment: initial !important; background-origin: initial !important; background-clip: initial !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(23, 23, 23); font-family: __Inter_f367f3, __Inter_Fallback_f367f3; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\">- Khách sạn theo tiêu chuẩn 2 khách/phòng hoặc 3 khách/phòng (khách thứ 3 kê giường phụ)</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: __Inter_f367f3, __Inter_Fallback_f367f3; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248); margin: 0.5rem 0px; color: rgb(23, 23, 23); text-align: justify; background-image: initial !important; background-position: initial !important; background-size: initial !important; background-repeat: initial !important; background-attachment: initial !important; background-origin: initial !important; background-clip: initial !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(23, 23, 23); font-family: __Inter_f367f3, __Inter_Fallback_f367f3; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\"> Tương đương 3 sao:</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: __Inter_f367f3, __Inter_Fallback_f367f3; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248); margin: 0.5rem 0px; color: rgb(23, 23, 23); text-align: justify; background-image: initial !important; background-position: initial !important; background-size: initial !important; background-repeat: initial !important; background-attachment: initial !important; background-origin: initial !important; background-clip: initial !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(23, 23, 23); font-family: __Inter_f367f3, __Inter_Fallback_f367f3; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\">• Đà Lạt: Anh Đức, Minh Phát, Lilac, Hoàng Minh Châu…</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: __Inter_f367f3, __Inter_Fallback_f367f3; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248); margin: 0.5rem 0px; color: rgb(23, 23, 23); text-align: justify; background-image: initial !important; background-position: initial !important; background-size: initial !important; background-repeat: initial !important; background-attachment: initial !important; background-origin: initial !important; background-clip: initial !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(23, 23, 23); font-family: __Inter_f367f3, __Inter_Fallback_f367f3; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\"> Tương đương 4 sao:</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: __Inter_f367f3, __Inter_Fallback_f367f3; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248); margin: 0.5rem 0px; color: rgb(23, 23, 23); text-align: justify; background-image: initial !important; background-position: initial !important; background-size: initial !important; background-repeat: initial !important; background-attachment: initial !important; background-origin: initial !important; background-clip: initial !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(23, 23, 23); font-family: __Inter_f367f3, __Inter_Fallback_f367f3; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\">• Nha Trang : Green Beach, Emerald Bay....</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: __Inter_f367f3, __Inter_Fallback_f367f3; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248); margin: 0.5rem 0px; color: rgb(23, 23, 23); text-align: justify; background-image: initial !important; background-position: initial !important; background-size: initial !important; background-repeat: initial !important; background-attachment: initial !important; background-origin: initial !important; background-clip: initial !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(23, 23, 23); font-family: __Inter_f367f3, __Inter_Fallback_f367f3; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\">- Vé tham quan theo chương trình</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: __Inter_f367f3, __Inter_Fallback_f367f3; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248); margin: 0.5rem 0px; color: rgb(23, 23, 23); text-align: justify; background-image: initial !important; background-position: initial !important; background-size: initial !important; background-repeat: initial !important; background-attachment: initial !important; background-origin: initial !important; background-clip: initial !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(23, 23, 23); font-family: __Inter_f367f3, __Inter_Fallback_f367f3; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\">- Ăn theo chương trình. Chuẩn ăn từ 120.000 – 150.000 vnđ/khách.</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: __Inter_f367f3, __Inter_Fallback_f367f3; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248); margin: 0.5rem 0px; color: rgb(23, 23, 23); text-align: justify; background-image: initial !important; background-position: initial !important; background-size: initial !important; background-repeat: initial !important; background-attachment: initial !important; background-origin: initial !important; background-clip: initial !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(23, 23, 23); font-family: __Inter_f367f3, __Inter_Fallback_f367f3; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\">- Hướng dẫn viên tiếng Việt suốt tuyến</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: __Inter_f367f3, __Inter_Fallback_f367f3; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248); margin: 0.5rem 0px; color: rgb(23, 23, 23); text-align: justify; background-image: initial !important; background-position: initial !important; background-size: initial !important; backgr