 rgb(248, 248, 248); margin: 0.5rem 0px; color: rgb(23, 23, 23); text-align: justify; background-image: initial !important; background-position: initial !important; background-size: initial !important; background-repeat: initial !important; background-attachment: initial !important; background-origin: initial !important; background-clip: initial !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(23, 23, 23); font-family: __Inter_f367f3, __Inter_Fallback_f367f3; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\">- Vé máy bay khứ hồi SGN – DAD – SGN.</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: __Inter_f367f3, __Inter_Fallback_f367f3; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248); margin: 0.5rem 0px; color: rgb(23, 23, 23); text-align: justify; background-image: initial !important; background-position: initial !important; background-size: initial !important; background-repeat: initial !important; background-attachment: initial !important; background-origin: initial !important; background-clip: initial !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(23, 23, 23); font-family: __Inter_f367f3, __Inter_Fallback_f367f3; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\">- Hành lý ký gửi: 20 kg, xách tay 7 kg/1 khách.</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: __Inter_f367f3, __Inter_Fallback_f367f3; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248); margin: 0.5rem 0px; color: rgb(23, 23, 23); text-align: justify; background-image: initial !important; background-position: initial !important; background-size: initial !important; background-repeat: initial !important; background-attachment: initial !important; background-origin: initial !important; background-clip: initial !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(23, 23, 23); font-family: __Inter_f367f3, __Inter_Fallback_f367f3; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\">- Khách sạn theo tiêu chuẩn 2 khách/phòng hoặc 3 khách/phòng.</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: __Inter_f367f3, __Inter_Fallback_f367f3; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248); margin: 0.5rem 0px; color: rgb(23, 23, 23); text-align: justify; background-image: initial !important; background-position: initial !important; background-size: initial !important; background-repeat: initial !important; background-attachment: initial !important; background-origin: initial !important; background-clip: initial !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(23, 23, 23); font-family: __Inter_f367f3, __Inter_Fallback_f367f3; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\">- Ăn theo chương trình, thực đơn món Việt (set menu).</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: __Inter_f367f3, __Inter_Fallback_f367f3; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248); margin: 0.5rem 0px; color: rgb(23, 23, 23); text-align: justify; background-image: initial !important; background-position: initial !important; background-size: initial !important; background-repeat: initial !important; background-attachment: initial !important; background-origin: initial !important; background-clip: initial !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(23, 23, 23); font-family: __Inter_f367f3, __Inter_Fallback_f367f3; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\">- Vé tham quan theo chương trình.</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: __Inter_f367f3, __Inter_Fallback_f367f3; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248); margin: 0.5rem 0px; color: rgb(23, 23, 23); text-align: justify; background-image: initial !important; background-position: initial !important; background-size: initial !important; background-repeat: initial !important; background-attachment: initial !important; background-origin: initial !important; background-clip: initial !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(23, 23, 23); font-family: __Inter_f367f3, __Inter_Fallback_f367f3; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\">- Hướng dẫn viên tiếng Việt nối tuyến.</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: __Inter_f367f3, __Inter_Fallback_f367f3; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248); margin: 0.5rem 0px; color: rgb(23, 23, 23); text-align: justify; background-image: initial !important; background-position: initial !important; background-size: initial !important; background-repeat: initial !important; background-attachment: initial !important; background-origin: initial !important; background-clip: initial !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(23, 23, 23); font-family: __Inter_f367f3, __Inter_Fallback_f367f3; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\">- Bảo hiểm du lịch với mức bồi thường cao nhất 120.000.000đ/vụ.</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: __Inter_f367f3, __Inter_Fallback_f367f3; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248); margin: 0.5rem 0px; color: rgb(23, 23, 23); text-align: justify; background-image: initial !important; background-position: initial !important; background-size: initial !important; background-repeat: initial !important; background-attachment: initial !important; background-origin: initial !important; background-clip: initial !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(23, 23, 23); font-family: __Inter_f367f3, __Inter_Fallback_f367f3; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\">- Nón Vietravel + Nước suối + Khăn lạnh.</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: __Inter_f367f3, __Inter_Fallback_f367f3; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248); margin: 0.5rem 0px; color: rgb(23, 23, 23); text-align: justify; background-image: initial !important; background-position: initial !important; background-size: initial !important; background-repeat: initial !important; background-attachment: initial !important; background-origin: initial !important; background-clip: initial !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(23, 23, 23); font-family: __Inter_f367f3, __Inter_Fallback_f367f3; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\">- Thuế VAT.</span>',1,'2026-01-30 18:52:10','2026-01-30 18:55:58',7990000.00,1),(4,'TATNH5259','Tây Ninh: